overview_description.description:
ActiveBAS is an international EaaS company dedicated to delivering low-carbon buildings. Our cost-effective solutions address all aspects of energy efficiency and sustainability, ensuring optimal IAQ even in the most demanding environments. HVAC Digital Twin is our cutting-edge technology that combines ML with Modelica to automatically regulate commercial HVAC systems for maximum comfort and energy savings.

Our vision is to deliver cost-effective solutions that address all aspects of energy efficiency and net-zero buildings. We envision ActiveBAS as the intelligence that ensures facilities run efficiently, minimizing carbon footprint and optimizing indoor air quality.

In order to extend our reach, we partner with IoT companies to create a win-win situation in which both parties can grow their businesses thanks to this collaboration.
